OL,5, A crackdown on rogue pedicab operators 
OL,6, in London has been announced in the    
OL,7, King's Speech.                         
OL,9,FThe government's Pedicabs (London) Bill
OL,10,Fwill hand Transport for London (TfL)   
OL,11,Fthe power to implement a licensing     
OL,12,Fregime.                                
OL,14,FTfL will also be able control fares,   
OL,15,Fensure drivers undergo criminal record 
OL,16,Fchecks and set safety standards.       
OL,18,FThere have been growing concerns about 
OL,19,Funsafe pedicabs and passengers being   
OL,20,Fripped off.                            
